OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDespite
OL,6,Flargely clear skies many places will
OL,7,Fhave another warm or very warm night,
OL,8,Fespecially in large towns and cities,
OL,9,Fwith the humid conditions persisting.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FGenerally sunny and very
OL,12,Fwarm or hot. Breezier than recently,
OL,13,Fespecially along the coast which will
OL,14,Fkeep temperatures cooler than inland
OL,15,Fand bring a chance of mist and low
OL,16,Fcloud.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
