OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FHot or
OL,6,Fvery hot Friday, thereafter
OL,7,Ftemperatures decreasing. Sunny spells
OL,8,FFriday and Saturday, with a chance of
OL,9,Fisolated thunderstorms. Cloudier
OL,10,FSunday and possibly patchy light rain.
